 e^Be^Ae^{-\frac12[B,A]}=e^Ae^Be^{-\frac12[A,B]}, 
 e^Be^A=e^Ae^Be^{-\frac12[A,B]}e^{\frac12[B,A]}=e^Ae^Be^{-\frac12[A,B]}e^{-\frac12[A,B]} =e^Ae^Be^{-[A,B]}. 
e^{A+B} = e^A e^B e^{-\frac12[A,B]}
A+B=B+A
e^A e^B e^{-\frac12[A,B]} = e^{A+B} = e^{B+A} = e^B e^A e^{-\frac12[B,A]} 
